<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Noble2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Noble,</orth> subst. 1) a nobleman: <cit><quote>a beggar's book outworths a --'s blood,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.123" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 123</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>will deserve a right good husband, let him be a n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.146" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 146</bibl></cit>. Often in the plural: <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.243" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 243</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.1.33" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.247" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 247</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.2.88" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 3, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.2.17" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.77" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.96" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 96</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.90" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 3, 90</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.129" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 129</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.172" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.209" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 2, 209</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.255" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.4.9" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.6.122" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 6, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.180" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 180</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 79</bibl> etc.<lb />2) a gold coin (worth 6 s. 8 d.): <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.167" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 112</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 112</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.23" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.82" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 82</bibl>. Quibbling with <cit><quote>royal:</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.317" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 317</bibl></cit>. 321; and perhaps <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.74" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 74</bibl>. With <cit><quote>angel:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 35</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>